column5: So, because Sunday was a beautiful day, I wanted to take my little puppy (boxer) out for a walk. This would be his 2nd walk outdoors.  Anyway, as I was out there - I drove past "Loafers Lake" in Brampton. Just a simple question here...  Anyone know what species are in there? I've tried searching on the internet and couldn't come up with anything. Any help would be much appreciated...
